{
  "stem": "25589.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And your father was told about that and came to find him, I think?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was out with Joe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Joe was out with me and Alan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were having a good time-- the tanks and everybody there, and the parade, and all that sort of stuff.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the meantime, this was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were rounding up all the bad people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like we used to call them the black shirts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had black shirts on, and they used to parade like the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to-- but we never, as kids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were there before the war, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we never thought any bad of them, because hey, they didn't bother us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they were-- they were bad people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the best thing I like to remember, though-- we got, we got out free, Scot free.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The only thing I feel bad, that the people-- and I'd like to dedicate this video to the people's life in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Their lives got wasted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Their lives got wasted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I would have liked to see them come back and tell their story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was the best part of the story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I like this project that Steve Spielberg-- that he donated such a-- his time, and the people that used this TV.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I hope a new generation will learn from this, and that they should understand that the pain that we went through and that we endured.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I hope they learn from it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they should have peace and love each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's important.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
